Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.30,0:01:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好今天我们也一起加油\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是快忍不住了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有反应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒在抖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热热的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.95,0:02:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手指摸你\N就抖成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用舌头怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.67,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的反应好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我直接舔吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.47,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么呻吟起来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.38,0:05:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有精液的味耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.24,0:06:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬邦邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.07,0:06:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我的屁股了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.61,0:06:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是感觉更兴奋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.56,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒热起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家也兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.84,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.42,0:08:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶和下面都看见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.50,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒请好好享受喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头也硬了，很有感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢舔睾丸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这姿势好害羞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.11,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经忍不住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.72,0:10:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我继续舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再撑一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.28,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能射喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不能能射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.69,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了，涨成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.36,0:14:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我让你射吗?\N我要吹更快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你射好多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.28,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再让你口爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.17,0:17:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们也尽情做爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.38,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想做什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.28,0:18:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉人家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不说..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.62,0:18:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.90,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以这样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不告诉我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.24,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.24,0:19:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头已经这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.04,0:20:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到我的奶顶到你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.58,0:20:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是只会舔奶头喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.94,0:21:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我舔肉棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.59,0:22:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也要我舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.01,0:22:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.15,0:22:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呻吟得好下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.09,0:22:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.86,0:23:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.93,0:23:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很敏感耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.00,0:23:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根肉棒最敏感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒涨起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.88,0:23:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要帮你脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.85,0:24:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这么大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.74,0:24:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家好想要肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.02,0:24:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.17,0:25:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.24,0:25:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又大又硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.76,0:27:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.63,0:27:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.40,0:27:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家的奶头也好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.70,0:28:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.87,0:29:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.32,0:29:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒还想给我吹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.29,0:30:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.26,0:31:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.49,0:31:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.32,0:33:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直吹着肉棒\N小穴也兴奋起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.20,0:33:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来做更淫荡的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.47,0:33:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我也爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.24,0:34:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿湿的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:20.73,0:34:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家想要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.67,0:34:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.02,0:34:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉好猛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.90,0:35:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.97,0:35:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶到最深处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.93,0:35:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒把小穴给塞满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.14,0:35:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:10.84,0:36:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.79,0:36:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.93,0:36:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停抽插了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.40,0:36:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根肉棒太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.09,0:37:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.03,0:37:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.90,0:38:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续干我可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.40,0:39:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒顶到子宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.69,0:39:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了，好有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.65,0:39:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以继续骑乘吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.93,0:40:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.81,0:41:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:33.16,0:41:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.23,0:41:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我推车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.04,0:41:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.98,0:41:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的大肉棒干进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.07,0:42:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒顶得好深喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:31.48,0:42:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.09,0:42:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒热热的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.40,0:43:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉好猛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.68,0:43:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了\N射我的嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:39.52,0:47:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再让你爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.41,0:48:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.02,0:48:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.15,0:48:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以跟其他男人做爱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:16.23,0:48:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:19.96,0:48:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.37,0:48:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就好好看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.17,0:48:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让你兴奋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.79,0:48:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:53.20,0:48:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们喇舌给他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:14.55,0:49:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，干嘛靠过来看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:33.37,0:49:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我要跟他做什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:42.18,0:49:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:49.39,0:49:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公你的趣的很变态耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:08.47,0:50:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这么涨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.10,0:50:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想吹这根大肉棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:00.93,0:51:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，你也没他硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:08.13,0:51:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:21.35,0:51:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.69,0:51:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道跟你的不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.18,0:52:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.72,0:52:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，这男人的很硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.06,0:52:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也兴奋了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:41.29,0:52:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:04.25,0:53:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这男人好像很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:10.12,0:53:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以继续吹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:21.20,0:53:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公你应该不介意吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:43.75,0:53:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹他的大肉棒我也兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:00.57,0:54:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才更硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:06.58,0:54:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的肉棒也许比你大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:02.37,0:55:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴已经湿起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:27.46,0:55:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着我的巨乳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.40,0:55:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也硬起来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.52,0:56:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用奶磨他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:31.32,0:57:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.13,0:57:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.60,0:57:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:57.88,0:58:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想继续看下去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:11.36,0:58:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一直吹这男人的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.30,0:58:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让他全部射给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:17.29,0:59:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这男人硬到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.33,1:00:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒硬邦邦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:03.33,1:00:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那老公的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.21,1:00:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的肉棒好涨，也许t射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:36.30,1:00:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.24,1:00:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，你要看着他射给我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.11,1:00:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想射?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.19,1:00:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公，真的可以?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:00.19,1:01:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都很变态耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:58.77,1:04:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一起射精，好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:38.94,1:04:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:00.30,1:05:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:21.18,1:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再射一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:26.12,1:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公给你看着特别兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.06,1:06:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着想看什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:13.10,1:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个大叔在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:25.11,1:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都硬起来了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:32.45,1:07:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔，为什么都硬了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.59,1:07:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:44.46,1:07:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做就兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:59.14,1:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.96,1:08:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很兴奋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.24,1:08:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热热的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:36.11,1:08:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:45.99,1:08:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:57.34,1:09:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒怎么硬成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:03.87,1:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想我做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.88,1:09:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉我为什么硬吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:13.08,1:09:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待我做什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:23.49,1:09:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要舔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:52.46,1:09:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:43.84,1:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:49.98,1:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要更爽吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.58,1:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吹更快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.14,1:13:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你们更爽耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.49,1:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的口技比其他女生更棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:18.06,1:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒有够大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.88,1:14:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:22.25,1:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘴巴里变更大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.17,1:16:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:13.56,1:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:18.90,1:17:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:23.31,1:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会想射了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:28.91,1:17:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:40.05,1:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:47.93,1:18:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:00.60,1:19:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.52,1:21:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒为什么这么涨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:05.72,1:22:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.75,1:22:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:32.42,1:22:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你吸干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:34.75,1:23:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:38.75,1:23:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还有一根吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:48.76,1:23:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:06.04,1:25:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全射给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.57,1:27:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴都是精液
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:24.04,1:27:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3根肉棒都射给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:31.92,1:27:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔\N下次想要爽可以再找我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.26,1:27:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再吹到你们射
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:59.28,1:28:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...我好想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:11.69,1:28:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:20.36,1:28:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了，好想要喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:32.64,1:28:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎样才给我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:36.65,1:28:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我兴奋我就给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:53.52,1:30:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要肉棒\N还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:10.21,1:30:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒已经硬起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:21.55,1:30:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只给你摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:29.56,1:30:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:43.57,1:30:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒热热的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:48.51,1:30:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么味道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:54.92,1:31:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒的味道好香
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:17.74,1:31:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:44.97,1:31:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:53.38,1:31:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:08.46,1:32:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:11.66,1:32:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我快忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:38.89,1:32:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒硬到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:43.03,1:32:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以舔一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:59.44,1:33:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:46.56,1:33:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很想吹?还不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:42.88,1:34:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:46.88,1:34:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:06.56,1:36:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想继续吹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:12.30,1:36:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想,,,\N给我慢慢的含进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:40.97,1:40:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:45.78,1:40:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要吗\N好想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:20.67,1:42:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快忍不住了，给我舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:48.97,1:42:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得好清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:03.65,1:43:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞..\N这里兴奋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:48.49,1:43:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:21.99,1:44:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:27.06,1:44:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再插深点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:24.46,1:45:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续让我爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:08.56,1:47:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:00.54,1:49:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶得好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:04.14,1:49:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再插深点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:26.56,1:49:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:32.30,1:49:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整根顶上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:54.99,1:50:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吹肉棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:54.39,1:50:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒顶得好深喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:28.55,1:51:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒硬到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:17.52,1:54:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:38.14,1:55:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要口爆你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:58.01,1:58:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续给我肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:02.68,1:58:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想吹
